[{"id":"VR834498","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows three small spheres arranged at the corners of an equilateral triangle of side length L. The charge of the small sphere at the top corner is positive 2 q. The charge of the small sphere at the bottom left corner is negative q. The charge of the small sphere at the bottom right corner is negative q. The side length of the equilateral triangle is labled L.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR834498.g01.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A system of three small, charged spheres consists of two negatively charged spheres, each of charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative q\"><math alttext=\"negative q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>-</mo><mi>q</mi></mpadded></math></span></span>, and one positively charged sphere of charge <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive 2 Q\"><math alttext=\"positive 2 Q\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>q</mi></mpadded></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. The spheres are fixed in place with their centers at the corners of an equilateral triangle of side length <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"L\"><math alttext=\"L\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>L</mi></math></span></span>. What is the electric potential energy of the three-sphere system?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR834498_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"positive the fraction with numerator 2 k q squared, and denominator L, end fraction\"><math alttext=\"positive the fraction with numerator 2 k q squared, and denominator L, end fraction\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>k</mi><msup><mi>q</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi>L</mi></mfrac></mpadded></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Zero</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative the fraction with numerator negative 3 k q squared, and denominator L, end fraction\"><math alttext=\"negative the fraction with numerator negative 3 k q squared, and denominator L, end fraction\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>k</mi><msup><mi>q</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi>L</mi></mfrac></mpadded></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative the fraction with numerator negative 5 k q squared, and denominator L, end fraction\"><math alttext=\"negative the fraction with numerator negative 5 k q squared, and denominator L, end fraction\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mpadded><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>5</mn><mi>k</mi><msup><mi>q</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mi>L</mi></mfrac></mpadded></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":2}]